currentDoc: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

currentSuggestions.original: In just 50 years, countries like Russia, Germany and even the U.S. had advanced beyond what they were in the 21st century.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: In just 50 years, countries like Russia, Germany and even the U.S. had advanced beyond what they were in the 21st century.

currentSuggestions.original: The story follows the lives of many different characters from several generations living in this new world.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: The story follows the lives of many different characters from several generations living in this new world.
